      "id": "SEC10",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Business Scenario"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "A company delivers products to more than 800 customer locations across South India. Instead of creating separate transportation lanes for each location, all customer locations are assigned to the 'South India' Transportation Zone. Transportation planning becomes significantly simpler."
    },
